data.description: NEW PRICE! This stunning custom built home in Guyton has everything on you wish list plus more. Exquisite landscaping & walkway leads you to a charming covered front porch featuring a wood ceiling. As you enter the home, you are welcomed by the warmth of the fireplace with detailed trim as well as coffered ceiling adding further depth to the room. Barn doors lead to the kitchen where you will find designer lighting, farmhouse sink with gooseneck faucet & specialty cabinetry (roll out shelving for pots/pans!) Cabinetry continues in the laundry room for ultimate organization. Primary suite is not to be missed with 3 closets! The lux bathroom includes fully tiled shower with rainhead, garden tub & stylish tilting mirrors with dual vanities. The backyard is an entertainer’s dream with extended covered porch & galvanized paneling for an intimate & chic space. Smart speakers in living spaces & patio add to the ambience while entertaining or relaxing after a long day. Shed for extra storage!
